From b8120c7585bbdfa6e3bdbecc6ee8952ba0f6accc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Javi <javi@example.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 17:05:12 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(P0-P3): senior review improvements
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

P0 (critical):
- Rename Cyrillic Alусti* files/identifiers to ASCII (Alusti, AlustiAbrev)
- Remove 6 .DS_Store committed files; expand .gitignore
- Add ErrorBoundary wrapping ScaleScreen (prevents white-screen on scale crash)
- Add README.md with clinical disclaimer + 31-scale catalog
- Add LICENSE (MIT)
- Add Vitest setup + 87 unit tests covering getScore/interpret for 10 critical
  scales (MMSE, MoCA, Barthel x2, Tinetti, Zarit, NPI-Q, PHQ-9, FRAIL, Rockwood)

P1 (high):
- ESLint (TS strict + React + a11y + Prettier) + .editorconfig + .prettierrc
- Self-host DM Sans + JetBrains Mono via @fontsource (no Google Fonts)
  for privacy + real offline
- Wrap saveFavorites/saveRecents with try/catch (QuotaExceededError safe)
- Code-split ScaleScreen with React.lazy per scale (-40% initial bundle)
- Add aria-labels to icon-only buttons + role=dialog + Escape + focus trap
  on ResultModal
- GitHub Actions CI: lint + typecheck + test + build on push/PR

P2 (medium):
- Convert UpdateBanner from inline styles to Tailwind
- Document onMarkDirty as intentional no-op (kept for compat with 31 scales)
- Remove misleading FIX #1/#4/#5 comments; real dedupe in addRecent
  (by scaleId+score+interpretation, not by timestamp)
- Add CSP meta + robots noindex + robots.txt (clinical privacy)
- Add 'Borrar recientes al cerrar la app' toggle in Settings
  (pagehide + visibilitychange listeners)

P3 (low):
- Refactor ScaleScreen switch to Record<string, Component> map (cleaner)
- Memoize SkinLayersSVG in NPUAP (React.memo)
- Expand Workbox globPatterns (woff2/woff/ttf) + 4MB limit for fonts

Verification:
- typecheck: PASS
- tests: 87/87 PASS (10 test files)
- build: PASS (87 precache entries, 60KB gz initial bundle)
- lint: 0 errors, 17 warnings (all pre-existing)
- prettier: PASS
